{"tid":2120340,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"狀元：「竊鈎者誅，竊國者侯」  在香港看不到曙光","createTime":"2020-07-22T15:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T15:33:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0d54a1a39ea82e821cbca528c0baf5ae189316f4","tid":2120340,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:26:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539333-20200722.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539333-20200722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=ce71b34c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539333-20200722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a914ed04\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539333-20200722.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n今年考獲7科5**的狀元，就讀聖保羅男女中學的黃摯毅，已經收到中大有條件取錄，修讀理學院分子細胞學，他同時希望副修中文。<br />\n<br />\n對中文有濃厚興趣的黃摯毅，被問到會以哪本文學作品形容香港現況時，引用了《莊子．胠篋》中「彼竊鈎者誅，竊國者為諸侯」，形容與香港情況相近。該句句子的意思指，偷取腰帶的人要被處刑，但篡奪政權的人卻能被封諸侯，批諷社會的不公義。<br />\n<br />\n黃摯毅指，於香港完成學士學位後，會考慮到外國升學，曾打算一直留在香港的他，指近年看見香港於法律上、施政方針上及人與人之間關係的轉變，整體大環境亦變差，「喺香港睇唔到好多曙光，亦見唔到好多光明」，會深思將來會否回港發展。"},{"pid":"12b6268cddba272008cd98ca418426053a59adda","tid":2120340,"uid":59570,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:31:52.000Z","msg":"希望長大咗唔好變民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c00dff2dc7dc6135d5ae371f2b1a19d8db716ae","tid":2120340,"uid":331739,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:33:22.000Z","msg":"究竟佢係講緊共匪定暴徒呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}